high_descs: Turn around, hang a left at the stove and walk to the green table on the left.
Pick up the egg in between the tomato and the glass bottle on the table.
Turn around and walk to the sink ahead.
Place the egg in the sink on the left side, rinse it for a few seconds, and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk to the green table ahead.
Put the rinsed egg on the table to the left of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed egg on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the edge of the green and white table.
Pick up the egg next to the tomato from the table.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Put the egg in the sink, fill the sink with water, and drain the water, picking the egg back up.
Turn around and walk to the green and white table.
Put the egg down on the table next to the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Wash an egg and put it back on the table.

high_descs: Turn right then turn right and go around to the other side of the table
Pick up the egg that is behind the tomato
Turn around and head to the sink
Put the egg in the sink and turn on the water, then turn off the water and pick up the egg from the sink
Turn around and go back to the table
Put the egg on the table
anns.task_desc: Put a washed egg on the table
